data.title: Electric motorcycles that are Soulful by Design
data.meta_description: LiveWire electric motorcycles are built for the urban experience, with the power and range to take you beyond. LiveWire comes from the lineage of Harley-Davidson, and our premium all-EV motorbikes are available for sale today.
data.text:
Financing offers available only on new LiveWire motorcycles financed through Eaglemark Savings Bank (ESB) and subject to credit approval. Not all applicants will qualify. Stated offers are available only to high credit tier customers at ESB. The APR may vary based on the applicant’s past credit performance and the term of the loan. For example, a 2024 S2 Del Mar® with an MSRP of $15,499, 10% down payment and amount financed of $13,949.10, 48-month repayment term, and 9.84% APR results in 47 monthly payments of $204.02 and a 48th balloon payment of $8,906.87. In this example, customer is responsible for applicable taxes, title, licensing fees and any other fees or charges at the time of sale. APR is calculated according to the simple interest method. Not valid in conjunction with other offers. Other terms, conditions, and limitations may apply. See your LiveWire Dealership or contact our team of LiveWire Gurus for details. This Financing Offer is valid during the period of July 1, 2024-August 31, 2024.

*Financing Offer available only on untitled 2024 S2 Del Mar and Mulholland motorcycles financed through Eaglemark Savings Bank (ESB) and is subject to credit approval. Not all applicants will qualify. 1.99% APR offer is available only to high credit tier customers at ESB and only for a 24 month term. The APR may vary based on the applicant’s past credit performance and the term of the loan. For example, a 2024 LiveWire® S2 Del Mar in Nimbus Gray or Nightfall Blue with an MSRP of $15,499, no down payment and amount financed of $15,499, 24 month repayment term, and 1.99% APR results in monthly payments of $659.26. A 2024 LiveWire® S2 Mulholland in Liquid Black with an MSRP of $15,999, no down payment and amount financed of $15,999, 24 month repayment term, and 1.99% APR results in monthly payments of $680.53. In these examples, customer is responsible for applicable taxes, title, licensing fees and any other fees or charges at the time of sale. APR is calculated according to the simple interest method. Not valid in conjunction with other offers. Other terms, conditions, and limitations may apply. Dealer participation may vary. Customer must take delivery by July 31, 2024. This Financing Offer is valid during the period of May 24, 2024, to August 31, 2024. Financing offer is subject to change or cancellation at anytime.

**Financing Offer available only on untitled 2024 S2 Del Mar motorcycles financed through Eaglemark Savings Bank (ESB) and is subject to credit approval. Not all applicants will qualify. 2.19% APR offer is available only to high credit tier customers at ESB and only for a 36-month term. The APR may vary based on the applicant’s past credit performance and the term of the loan. For example, a 2024 LiveWire™ S2 Del Mar in Nimbus Grey or Nightfall Blue with an MSRP of $15,499, 10% down payment and amount financed of $13,949.10, 36-month repayment term, and 2.19% APR results in 35 monthly payments of $149.09 and a 36th balloon payment of $9,502.70. In this example, customer is responsible for applicable taxes, title, licensing fees and any other fees or charges at the time of sale. APR is calculated according to the simple interest method. Not valid in conjunction with other offers. Other terms, conditions, and limitations may apply. Dealer participation may vary. Customer must take delivery by July 31, 2024. This Financing Offer is valid during the period of July 1, 2024, to August 31, 2024. Financing offer is subject to change or cancellation at anytime.
